and resolve property and debt related issues individual transaction size is generally  mm and greater geographic focus is the continental us and hawaii   castle hill partners the castle   west th street austin tx  background castle hill partners is managed and owned by principals whom have spent their professional careers in property development operations and financial workouts the firm has collectively acquired and developed over  million square feet of office and industrial space over  units of multifamily and more than  acres of commercial and residential land the firm has an extensive history in bankruptcy resolution financial restructure and administration of nonperforming cre debt castle hill partners has acquired over b in performing and nonperforming debt instruments in its history geographic distribution of debt and property assets cover fortytwo states in the continental us and hawaii during the past twenty years chp has been capitalized by top us institutional investors including most of the major wall street investment banking firms investment activity in distressed debt dates to the early ’s during the us savings  loan crisis   the firm has been a principal in multiple partnerships with us federal agencies which include the rtc and fdic serving as investor and operating general partner chp has consistently experienced successful investment performance during a period which covers three major market cycles partial list includes both current and previously owned investments investments listings  map property name type location    kingland landtimber texas deerfield multifamily redevelopment florida woods of mandarin multifamily redevelopment florida cross creek multifamily redevelopment florida club at charter point multifamily redevelopment florida city ridge multifamily redevelopment florida caroline square multifamily redevelopment florida trinity falls master planned community texas airport commerce park industrial texas heron cove office new hampshi